### Key features demonstrated

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **Tenant switching** | SegmentedButton in AppBar + RadioListTile in Settings |
| **Streaming responses** | SSE stream parsing via HTTP streamed response |
| **Non-streaming fallback** | Auto-falls back to POST if streaming fails |
| **Citations** | Numbered source badges with relevance percentage |
| **Feedback** | 👍/👎 buttons calling feedback API |
| **Offline indicator** | Connection status banner + cloud_off icon |
| **Server configuration** | Configurable URL in Settings |
| **Health check** | Test Connection button with live server status display |
| **Usage stats** | Request count, latency, grounding score from API |
| **RAG toggle** | FilterChip to enable/disable retrieval |
| **Sample questions** | Tappable domain-specific questions on empty state |
| **Markdown rendering** | flutter_markdown for formatted responses |
| **Persistent preferences** | SharedPreferences for tenant, URL, options |
| **State management** | Provider pattern with ChangeNotifier |
| **Auto-clear on tenant switch** | Messages clear when switching tenants |
| **Loading state** | Spinner on send button + linear progress in bubble |
| **Tenant theming** | Blue for SIS, green for MFG throughout |

