### Differences from the web app (intentional for mobile)

| Aspect | Web | Mobile |
|---|---|---|
| Streaming | EventSource API | HTTP streamed response parsing |
| Layout | Side-by-side panels | Single column, bottom nav |
| Compare mode | Two chat panels | Not included (screen too small) |
| Monitoring | Full dashboard | Stats in Settings screen |
| Offline | N/A | Connection banner + offline indicator |
| Server URL | Proxied via Next.js | Configurable in Settings |

